thread.title: BRIEF-Societe Francaise De Casinos FY Net Profit Group Share Up At 1.1 Million Euros

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Societe Francaise De Casinos FY Net Profit Group Share Up At 1.1 Million Euros

organizations.name: brief-societe francaise de casinos fy net profit group

text:
April 3 (Reuters) - SOCIETE FRANCAISE DE CASINOS SA :
* FY NET PROFIT GROUP SHARE EUR 1.1 MILLION VERSUS EUR 0.5 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY CURRENT OPERATING RESULT EUR 653,000 VERSUS EUR 495,000 YEAR AGO
* FY EBITDA EUR 2.4 MILLION VERSUS EUR 1.7 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY REVENUE EUR 26.6 MILLION VERSUS EUR 22.0 MILLION YEAR AGO
* HOPES TO OPEN THE CASINO IN BAGNÃˆRES-DE-LUCHON BEFORE THE END OF THE YEAR 2018
